      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 32 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 32 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>恆，亨，无咎，利貞，利有攸往。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Heng indicates successful progress and no error (in what it denotes). But the advantage will come from being firm and correct; and movement in any direction whatever will be advantageous.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
