      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 32 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 32 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：浚恆，貞凶，无攸利。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows its subject deeply (desirous) of long continuance. Even with firm correctness there will be evil; there will be no advantage in any way.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
